                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/updates-tianjin-wris-side-event-focuses-tools-low-carbon-pathway-china">Updates from Tianjin: WRI‚Äôs Side Event Focuses on Tools for a Low-Carbon Pathway in China</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/bikes_10-12-10.jpg" alt="" title="" width="164" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
