                <span class="field-content"><a href="../library/tianjin-briefing-oct-5-2010-seligsohn-industrial-efficiency">Tianjin Briefing Oct. 5, 2010: Seligsohn - Industrial Efficiency</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/Seligsohn&#32;-&#32;Industrial&#32;Efficiency&#32;-&#32;Tianjin&#32;Oct&#32;2010-1.jpg" alt="" title="" width="160" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
