  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>Download from the link above &#8220;From Grey to Green: Making China‚Äôs Rapid Urbanization Sustainable&#8221;, a presentation by ChinaFAQs Expert <a href="../expert/deborah-seligsohn">Deborah Seligsohn</a> from <a href="../blog-posts/wri-hosts-coal-use-china-future-use-and-emissions-control-briefing-tianjin-china">&#8220;Coal Use in China: Future Use and Emissions Control&#8221;</a>, A Briefing in Tianjin, China on October 5, 2010.</p></div>
